      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Older vehicle in poor condition and priced accordingly. It has noticeable cosmetic wear inside and out, and buyers should expect mechanical needs, deferred maintenance, and the possibility of repairs before it can be depended on as a regular driver. Best suited for someone looking for a cheap project, parts car, or basic transportation with work. Please come inspect it carefully and plan on buying it as-is.",
